<item>
            <title>[STORM-3162] Race condition at updateHeartbeatCache</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-3162</link>
                <project id="12314820" key="STORM">Apache Storm</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is discovered during testing for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-3133&quot; title=&quot;Extend metrics on Nimbus and LogViewer&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;STORM-3133&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;STORM-3133&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Travis-CI log can be found &lt;a href=&quot;https://travis-ci.org/apache/storm/jobs/408719153#L1897&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Specifically, updateHeartbeatCache can be invoked both by Nimbus (at `Nimbus#updateHeartBeats`) and by Supervisor (at `Nimbubs#updateCachedHeartbeatsFromWorker` at `Nimbus#updateCachedHeartbeatsFromSupervisor`), causing ConcurrentModificationException.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
